Text:
thank you, so much!
this is a great series
Would you have One More Bite & Bite Marks please

I noticed at the end of book 8, deadliest bite, that the author, jennifer rardin, passed away september, 2010.  the 8 books in the jaz parks series are her complete work.  could you put them all out together?  I really enjoyed this series... RIP  jennifer rardin.
